.Dt HYPERV 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm hyperv
.Nd Hyper-V guest nexus device
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "hyperv0 at pvbus?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
driver performs Synthetic Interrupt Controller initialization,
sets up hypercalls,
and provides access to VMBus services required by paravirtualized
devices such as disk and network interfaces.
